	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I made a small fix since yesterday.
<br />
<br />I excluded non-Nintendo mappers (as I said in my 1st post), and it's true I excluded CPROM too because it's very specific. Switching CHR-RAM pages is interesting but doing it while being limited to 32kb PRG-ROM is not.
<br />
<br />Also I don't really recommend MMC2/4, I just included them so I could include (almost) all Nintendo mappers in the chart. I just add them at an option when I recommend the MMC1.
<br />
<br />PS : Tepples, your table is great and is a great addition to the wiki.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
